                     <interp inst="t18010218-72-defend427" type="age" value="28"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18010218-72-off392" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010218-72-off392" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010218-72-off392" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010218-72-cd393" type="crimeDate">20th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010218-72-off392 t18010218-72-cd393"></join>, a coat, value 8s. two pair of breeches, value 15s. two waistcoats, value 8s. a pair of cotton drawers, value 6d. a pair of stockings, value 2s. two pocket-handkerchiefs, value 6d. a pocket-book, value 5s. a silver pencil, value 1s. 6d. two half-guineas, and two seven-shilling-pieces, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18010218-72-victim429" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Bradburn
                        <interp inst="t18010218-72-victim429" type="surname" value="Bradburn"></interp>
