                     <interp inst="t18010218-72-verdict396" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               Of stealing goods, value 39s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18010218-72-punish397" type="punishmentDescription">
